Were they? One point emphasized in the interview is that 3AC was=C2=A0not=
=C2=A0really a hedge fund, but a proprietary trading firm; for the most par=
t, it did not take outside money and used its partners=E2=80=99 capital. No=
body was paying 3AC to take risks with their money. Instead, 3AC was paying=
