<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Apparently the way it works is that if you blo=
w up a big crypto firm,=C2=A0you have to sit in your home in a crypto-frien=
dly jurisdiction giving long rambling interviews about your failures to eve=
ryone who wants to chat. Arguably this is an improvement over traditional f=
inance, where if you blow up a financial institution you keep quiet and lea=
ve the talking to your lawyers. (=E2=80=9CSam Bankman-Fried Should Shut Up,=
